Reports have surfaced that police have cuffed an actor on the soapie Scandal! at a Springs brothel. eNCA reports that 16 other people, including six men and 11 women, were arrested at the brothel in the east of Johannesburg and have been charged under the Sexual Offences Act. Channel24, meanwhile, reports that e.tv said it was aware of the &#8220;stories and speculation surrounding the arrest of an actor&#8221; but said it had not received further details at this stage and would allow due process to follow. ALSO READ: Man sentenced to over 300 years&#8217; imprisonment for rape For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter.